Subject: RE: [VB] Tranny question

You will need to remove the transaxle.There is a splined sleeve with a gear on it to hold the input shaft to the main shaft of the trans.I forgot which redux box will need to be taken apart to get the side cover off for access to the input shaft joint.When installing a NEW snap ring safety wire the eyes together after install.

